Editor biographies


Monica Daley received her BS degree in Biology at University of Utah, USA in 1999, and her PhD from Harvard University, MA, USA in 2006.&amp;nbsp; She held an NSF Postdoctoral Fellowship at the University of Michigan from 2006-2008, and a faculty position in the Structure and Motion Lab...">




    



